        Resident Illustrator/Animator, Shorter than Short Form (STSF)
        BuzzFeed Video is looking for an Illustrator/Animator Resident to come work with our Shorter than Short Form (STSF) Team creating content for Snapchat. The ideal candidate is creative, can think quickly on their feet, and loves the Snapchat platform. This position will produce 3-5 Snapchat pieces per day.
        This is a 3-month temporary assignment in our Los Angeles office. We offer free lunch, free snacks, and social events ranging from movie screenings to happy hours.
        Requirements:
        * Brainstorm and illustrate ideas quickly and effectively
        * Willingness to learn quickly from metrics and reiterate on what we learn
        * Experience with Photoshop, After Effects and Illustrator
        * Experience with Premier and Cinema 4D are a huge plus!
        * Uses Snapchat on a daily basis and LOVES the platform
        * Loves to work quickly and efficiently
        * NO HATERS!
        Application: Along with your resume, please provide the hyperlink to your website, blog, work, etc. We want to see what you have produced!
        About BuzzFeed
        BuzzFeed is the leading independent digital media and tech company delivering news and entertainment content to a global audience. We have offices in 18 cities around the world and more than 1300 employees including reporters, video producers, data scientists, engineers, brand strategists, and more. We infuse hard work and fun though a culture of experimentation, teamwork, equality, and humble confidence. As an employee, you'll enjoy perks like office events, snacks, career development courses, and no work on your birthday! But most importantly, you'll work with inspiring colleagues to build tools and create content that helps connect people all over the world.